<section id="about" class="about">
  <header>
    <h2>About Me</h2>
  </header>

  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="about__content">
      <div class="bg-pattern-ring"></div>
      <picture>
        <source
          media="(min-width: 800px)"
          srcset="/images/avatar-desktop.webp"
          width="100%"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/avatar-mobile.webp"
          alt="A man sitting behind a sunset, relaxed, with an amazing smile."
          width="450px"
        />
      </picture>

      <div class="about__text">
        <p>
          I'm Johnny Estrada, a web developer with about three years in the
          coding game. I have experience working with <span class="green"
            >React</span
          >, <span class="green">TypeScript</span>, <span class="green"
            >Tailwind</span
          >, <span class="green">Express</span>, <span class="green"
            >Node.js</span
          >, and <span class="green">MySQL</span>, but am front-end focused.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm currently working on an <a href="#projects"
            >issue tracking web app</a
          >, and I'm eagerly anticipating its release! This project has proven
          to be a significant turning point, offering a practical outlet for my
          skills and serving as a valuable learning ground. Stay tuned for the
          release, or just <a href="#contact">send a hello!</a>
        </p>

        <p>
          Beyond coding, I'm a 3D printing enthusiast fascinated by its
          possibilities. I also enjoy being outdoors, where you can find me
          paddleboarding in the bay.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .about {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 80px 0;

    h2 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: var(--main-heading);
      line-height: 40px;
      letter-spacing: -1.13636px;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 600px) {
      &.about {
        padding: 100px 0;
      }

      h2 {
        margin-bottom: 120px;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      &.about {
        padding: 120px 0;
      }
    }

    &__content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-width: 100%;
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    .green {
      color: var(--accent-green-400);
    }

    @media (min-width: 800px) {
      &__content {
        flex-direction: row;
      }
    }

    &__text {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    img {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 600px) {
      img {
        max-width: 100%;
        max-height: 400px;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      img {
        max-width: 540px;
        max-height: 500px;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 1043px) {
      img {
        padding-right: 30px;
      }
    }

    h3 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: var(--step-0);
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      margin: 10px 0 10px 0;
    }

    p {
      max-width: 445px;
      color: var(--stone-300);
      font-size: var(--body-text);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
    }

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      p {
        max-width: 500px;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 600px) {
      h3 {
        margin-top: 0px;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 800px) {
      h3,
      p {
        text-align: left;
      }
    }

    a {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 26px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: var(--text-white);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-green-400);
      width: 120px;
      height: 42px;
      margin: 0 auto;

      &:hover {
        color: var(--accent-green-400);
        transition: color 200ms ease-in-out;
      }

      &:focus {
        color: var(--accent-green-400);
      }

      &:active {
        color: var(--text-white);
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 600px) {
      a {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }

    /**************************/
    /*** Background Images ***/
    /************************/

    .bg-pattern-ring {
      background-image: url('/icons/pattern-rings.svg');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      width: 50%;
